Global Composite Release Liners Market Insights
Composite Release Liners Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Composite Release Liners Market Overview
The global composite release liners market is valued at approximately USD 3.2 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow at a CAGR of 5.4% over the forecast period of 2025-2030. The demand for composite release liners is primarily driven by the growing packaging industry, particularly in sectors such as food, pharmaceuticals, and electronics. Release liners are used in these industries for their critical role in ensuring the safe and efficient packaging of products. The market is also influenced by technological advancements in liner materials and coatings that enhance performance and sustainability.

